definition: to change/to become different/to transform/to vary/rebellion

sentences.english: In the second variation, writing a row means modifying an existing row.
sentences.chinese: 在第二个变体中，写一行意味着修改一个现有的行。

sentences.english: So we think the dwarf mutant "DDF-1" was GA insensitive.
sentences.chinese: 所以我们认为它是赤霉素相关突变体。

sentences.english: Most are variants of what is described in academia as "multi-attribute utility analysis."
sentences.chinese: 大多数是变体在学术界认为“多属性效用分析。”

sentences.english: Maori English is a variety of English used by Maori people.
sentences.chinese: 毛利英语是一种英语变体，为毛利人所使用。

sentences.english: Add any additional terms and their variants.
sentences.chinese: 添加任何其他术语及其变体。

sentences.english: Some say it is a modern variant of the kudu horn used traditionally in southern African culture.
sentences.chinese: 有人说它是南非传统的纰角鹿喇叭的现代变体。

sentences.english: The Sun Salutations are a variation of ballistic stretching.
sentences.chinese: 拜日式是弹性伸展的变体。

sentences.english: Always use this variant for characters who play psionic monsters.
sentences.chinese: 当灵能怪物作为角色出现时本变体规则总是适用。

sentences.english: Another variant is presented by some members of the Palmae.
sentences.chinese: 在一些棕榈科成员中还存在另一种变体。

sentences.english: Each variety had a different structure of rewards for winning, losing, or drawing.
sentences.chinese: 每一个变体各有不同的输赢或平局的奖励结构。

sentences.english: These morphs were then rated for attractiveness by 77 heterosexual male students.
sentences.chinese: 然后，77名异性恋男生对这些变体评定吸引力情况。

sentences.english: A strategy of shotgun antisense gene silencing was used to generate a rice mutant library.
sentences.chinese: 尝试利用鸟枪反义基因沉默策略构建水稻突变体库。

sentences.english: The sample above is a trivial variation of the QuickStart app.
sentences.chinese: 上面的例子是《快速起步》应用的一个简单的变体。

sentences.english: Objective To construct N-linked glycosylation site mutants of hantavirus.
sentences.chinese: 目的构建汉坦病毒糖基化位点的突变体。

sentences.english: The dwarf mutant was obtained from transgenic rice KMD with a crylAb gene.
sentences.chinese: 从转基因水稻“克螟稻”中获得了一个矮秆突变体。

sentences.english: Sweet corn is an endosperm mutant which was controled by single recessive gene or multi-recessive genes.
sentences.chinese: 甜玉米受一个或多个隐性基因控制的胚乳突变体。

definition: standard form (of a Chinese character)/plain font style (as opposed to bold or italic)/printed style (as opposed to cursive)/(Tw) traditional (i.e. unsimplified) characters
semantic component of a phono-semantic character (e.g. component刂[dao1] in 刻[ke4])
